txt.en: You have defeated many of the Dourhands loyal to the Iron Crown at Mur Shatraug in Câr Bronach.

Dourhands can be found at Mur Shatraug in Câr Bronach.\n\nEncamped at Mur Shatraug, the Witch-gate, the Dourhands loyal to the Iron Crown dutifully guard the pass to Câr Bronach. You should defeat Dourhand Dwarves.
Mur Shatraug: Watchers at the Witch-gate
You have done much to combat the Dourhands in service of the Iron Crown at Mur Shatraug, the Witch-gate.
Encamped at Mur Shatraug, the Witch-gate, the Dourhands loyal to the Iron Crown dutifully guard the pass to Câr Bronach.

After exploring Mur Shatraug, the Witch-gate, you have discovered Dourhands loyal to the Iron Crown guarding the pass to Câr Bronach. If the conquest of Mount Gundabad is to succeed, the Iron Crown and their wicked allies must be defeated and driven from the Mountain-home and its surrounding lands.\n\nYou should defeat Dourhand Dwarves at Mur Shatraug.
